---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			.hero {
				text-align: center;
				padding: 2rem 0;
				background: var(--card-gradient);
				border-radius: 20px;
				margin: 2rem 0;
				border: 1px solid rgba(var(--purple-200), 0.5);
				box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
			}
			.hero h1 {
				color: var(--primary-dark);
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 1rem;
			}
			.hero h1 i {
				color: var(--accent);
				margin-right: 0.5rem;
				background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--accent), var(--secondary));
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
				background-clip: text;
			}
			.content-card {
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				margin: 1.5rem 0;
				border: 1px solid rgba(var(--purple-200), 0.3);
				box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
				backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
			}
			.content-card:hover {
				border-color: rgba(var(--accent), 0.4);
				transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
			}
			a {
				color: var(--accent);
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
			}
			a:hover {
				color: var(--accent-dark);
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
			code {
				background: rgba(var(--purple-100), 0.8);
				color: var(--primary-dark);
				font-weight: 500;
			}
			ul {
				background: rgba(var(--blue-50), 0.5);
				border-radius: 8px;
				padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
				border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="hero">
				<h1><i class="fas fa-wave-square"></i> Welcome to Synthwave</h1>
				<p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: rgba(var(--gray-dark), 0.8);">
					Where AI meets creativity in the digital frontier
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="content-card">
				<h2 style="color: var(--primary-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem;">About Synthwave</h2>
				<p>
					Hey there! I'm <strong>Siyabonga Lukhele</strong>, but you might know me as <strong>siyabuilds</strong>. 
					I created Synthwave because I believe we're living in an extraordinary time where AI isn't just 
					changing how we workâ€”it's revolutionizing how we think, create, and share ideas.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="content-card">
				<h3 style="color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Why AI-Powered Blogging?</h3>
				<p>
					Traditional blogging has its limits. But when you combine human creativity with AI's vast 
					knowledge and processing power, magic happens. Synthwave is my experiment in pushing the 
					boundaries of what's possible when we collaborate with AI to create compelling, insightful, 
					and genuinely helpful content.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="content-card">
				<h3 style="color: var(--secondary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">What You'll Find Here</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Deep dives into AI tools and technologies that actually matter</li>
					<li>Creative experiments at the intersection of code and imagination</li>
					<li>Practical insights from building with cutting-edge tech</li>
					<li>Behind-the-scenes looks at how AI can enhance human creativity</li>
					<li>Honest takes on the future we're building together</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="content-card">
				<h3 style="color: var(--accent-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Join the Journey</h3>
				<p>
					Whether you're a developer, creator, or just someone curious about where technology is 
					heading, Synthwave is your window into the future we're building. Every post here is 
					crafted with AI assistance but driven by human vision and experience.
				</p>
				<p>
					Ready to explore? Check out my <a href="/blog">latest posts</a> or learn more 
					<a href="/about">about me and this project</a>.
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
